response.overview: In this workplace comedy, Warsan, the lone Muslim employee, becomes an accidental exorcist when tasked by her boss to perform a ‘spiritual purification' of the office, after multiple complaints of paranormal activity in the lunchroom. With absolutely no clue about the supernatural and armed only with faith and funny misunderstandings, she embarks on a comical journey to evict mischievous spirits- with one goal in mind: don’t get fired.
response.title: Unqualified
